title: Marvel NOW! Week 53 11/20/2013
description:
Hi folks! As per usual, I didn't see a collected torrent for this week's Marvel NOW! titles yet, so I thought I'd upload one. Included are:

A+X 014
Avengers 023
Avengers A.I. 006
Cable and X-Force 016
Daredevil 033
Fantastic Four 014
Indestructible Hulk 015 (finally! now I can put up Age of Ultron in reading order)
Longshot Saves the Marvel Universe 002 (of 4)
Secret Avengers 011
Superior Spider-Man Annual 001
Superior Spider-Man Team-Up 006
Thunderbolts 018
Uncanny X-Men 014
X-Men Legacy 020
X-Men 007 (license to thrill! awww yeeahh)

If you like them and have the money, buy them and support your favorite writers, artists, local comic shops and publishers. Thanks be to all the uploaders and scanners and seeders out there!
